OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fslowly dying out this evening. Then
OL,7,Fthe rest of the night will be dry with
OL,8,Fvariable amounts of cloud. A cold
OL,9,Fnight with patchy frost.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FA generally dry day with some
OL,12,Fbright or sunny spells and variable
OL,13,Fcloud, the odd spot of rain possible
OL,14,Fin the east. Light winds. Patchy rain
OL,15,Fin the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
