OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FSome
OL,6,Frain in the early hours of Monday
OL,7,Fotherwise it will be dry and bright.
OL,8,FBright spells and a few showers early
OL,9,Fand late on Tuesday. Scattered showers
OL,10,Fon Wednesday.
